The paper proposes a new encoder for machine comprehension tasks, which involves natural language processing and deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper focuses on learning representations and modeling relationships, which are common themes in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of gating vectors, which are commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on three datasets that involve text and image comprehension, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV).
